| Pricing Model         | Best For                        | Cost Optimization Strategy                           |
|-----------------------|---------------------------------|------------------------------------------------------|
| Pay-per-call          | Variable, unpredictable usage   | Implement aggressive caching and batching            |
| Monthly subscription  | Consistent, predictable volume  | Right-size tier based on actual usage data           |
| Tiered volume         | Growing businesses              | Monitor usage to upgrade/downgrade at optimal times  |
| Flat-rate unlimited   | High-volume power users         | Maximize value through comprehensive integration     |
| Hybrid models         | Mixed use cases                 | Separate production and development environments     |
